ly\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Verify publish method signature and structure\n- [ ] Verify publish method accepts workspace_path: Path parameter\n- [ ] Verify publish method accepts **options: Any parameter\n- [ ] Verify return type is Dict[str, Any]\n- [ ] Verify method loads metadata using metadata_service.load_metadata\n- [ ] Verify method calls _prepare_image_for_publishing\n- [ ] Verify method calls appropriate provider publish method\n- [ ] Verify method calls _update_publish_metadata\n- [ ] Verify method returns agent_info dictionary\n\n**Verification**: Review publish_runtime.py and verify method implementation matches design\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Verify _prepare_image_for_publishing method\n- [ ] Verify method checks metadata.build_mode\n- [ ] Verify method calls _prepare_local_image for \"local\" mode\n- [ ] Verify method calls _prepare_cloud_image for \"cloud\" mode\n- [ ] Verify method returns image_url string\n- [ ] Verify error handling for invalid build_mode\n\n**Verification**: Run unit test for _prepare_image_for_publishing with both local and cloud modes\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: Verify _prepare_local_image method\n- [ ] Verify method validates Docker is available\n- [ ] Verify method gets image_url from options or metadata\n- [ ] Verify method raises ValueError if image_url is missing\n- [ ] Verify method tags image for registry\n- [ ] Verify method pushes image to registry\n- [ ] Verify method uses authentication if provided\n- [ ] Verify method returns pushed image URL\n- [ ] Verify comprehensive error handling and logging\n\n**Verification**: Create test workspace with local image and verify image is pushed successfully\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: Verify _prepare_cloud_image method\n- [ ] Verify method gets cloud_provider from options or metadata\n- [ ] Verify method raises ValueError if cloud_provider is missing\n- [ ] Verify method calls cloud provider API (or raises NotImplementedError)\n- [ ] Verify method returns image URL from cloud provider\n- [ ] Verify error handling for cloud API failures\n\n**Verification**: Review implementation and verify appropriate error messages\n\n---\n\n### Task 7: Verify _publish_cr_to_k8s method (AgentCube provider)\n- [ ] Verify method validates router_url is present\n- [ ] Verify method validates workload_manager_url is present\n- [ ] Verify method gets namespace from options or defaults to \"default\"\n- [ ] Verify method creates AgentCubeProvider instance\n- [ ] Verify method calls provider.deploy_agent_runtime with correct parameters:\n  - [ ] agent_name\n  - [ ] image_url\n  - [ ] port\n  - [ ] entrypoint\n  - [ ] env_vars\n  - [ ] workload_manager_url\n  - [ ] router_url\n  - [ ] readiness_probe_path\n  - [ ] readiness_probe_port\n- [ ] Verify method generates session_id\n- [ ] Verify method returns agent_info dictionary with:\n  - [ ] agent_id\n  - [ ] agent_endpoint\n  - [ ] session_id\n  - [ ] namespace\n  - [ ] image_url\n  - [ ] provider\n- [ ] Verify comprehensive error handling\n\n**Verification**: Run integration test with AgentCube provider\n\n---\n\n### Task 8: Verify _publish_k8s method (Kubernetes provider)\n- [ ] Verify method gets namespace from options or defaults to \"default\"\n- [ ] Verify method gets replicas from options or defaults to 1\n- [ ] Verify method gets node_port from options\n- [ ] Verify method validates node_port range (30000-32767)\n- [ ] Verify method creates KubernetesProvider instance\n- [ ] Verify method calls provider.deploy_agent with correct parameters:\n  - [ ] agent_name\n  - [ ] image_url\n  - [ ] port\n  - [ ] entrypoint\n  - [ ] replicas\n  - [ ] node_port\n  - [ ] env_vars\n- [ ] Verify method generates session_id\n- [ ] Verify method waits for deployment to be ready\n- [ ] Verify method returns agent_info dictionary with:\n  - [ ] deployment_name\n  - [ ] service_name\n  - [ ] namespace\n  - [ ] service_url\n  - [ ] provider\n  - [ ] replicas\n  - [ ] node_port\n  - [ ] image_url\n- [ ] Verify comprehensive error handling\n\n**Verification**: Run integration test with Kubernetes provider\n\n---\n\n### Task 9: Verify _update_publish_metadata method\n- [ ] Verify method loads metadata from workspace\n- [ ] Verify method updates agent_id if present in agent_info\n- [ ] Verify method updates session_id if present in agent_info\n- [ ] Verify method updates k8s_deployment if present in agent_info\n- [ ] Verify method updates agent_endpoint if present in agent_info\n- [ ] Verify method saves updated metadata using metadata_service.save_metadata\n- [ ] Verify method logs metadata update\n\n**Verification**: Run publish command and verify metadata file is updated correctly\n\n---\n\n### Task 10: Verify _generate_session_id method\n- [ ] Verify method uses secrets.choice for random character selection\n- [ ] Verify method uses ASCII letters and digits\n- [ ] Verify method generates 32-character string\n- [ ] Verify session IDs are unique (run multiple times)\n- [ ] Verify session IDs are URL-safe\n\n**Verification**: Run method multiple times and verify uniqueness and length\n\n---\n\n### Task 11: Verify AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime method\n- [ ] Verify method ensures namespace exists\n- [ ] Verify method sanitizes agent name for Kubernetes\n- [ ] Verify method gets workload_manager_url from parameter or environment\n- [ ] Verify method gets router_url from parameter or environment\n- [ ] Verify method validates required URLs\n- [ ] Verify method creates AgentRuntime CR with correct spec:\n  - [ ] apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n  - [ ] kind: AgentRuntime\n  - [ ] metadata.name\n  - [ ] metadata.namespace\n  - [ ] spec.image\n  - [ ] spec.port\n  - [ ] spec.entrypoint\n  - [ ] spec.env\n  - [ ] spec.workloadManagerURL\n  - [ ] spec.routerURL\n  - [ ] spec.sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n  - [ ] spec.maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n  - [ ] spec.readinessProbe.path\n  - [ ] spec.readinessProbe.port\n  - [ ] spec.imagePullSecrets\n- [ ] Verify method handles 409 conflict by updating exi