method logs progress\n- [ ] Verify default timeout is 120 seconds\n\n**Verification**: Deploy test agent and verify method waits correctly\n\n---\n\n### Task 15: Verify KubernetesProvider._create_deployment method\n- [ ] Verify method creates V1Container with correct configuration\n- [ ] Verify method creates V1PodTemplateSpec\n- [ ] Verify method creates V1DeploymentSpec\n- [ ] Verify method creates V1Deployment\n- [ ] Verify method handles 409 conflict by updating\n- [ ] Verify method returns deployment dictionary\n\n**Verification**: Review deployment creation logic\n\n---\n\n### Task 16: Verify KubernetesProvider._create_service method\n- [ ] Verify method creates V1Service with correct configuration\n- [ ] Verify method sets type to NodePort\n- [ ] Verify method sets port mapping\n- [ ] Verify method handles custom node_port if provided\n- [ ] Verify method handles 409 conflict by updating\n- [ ] Verify method returns V1Service object\n\n**Verification**: Review service creation logic\n\n---\n\n### Task 17: Verify DockerService.push_image method\n- [ ] Verify method accepts image_name, registry_url, username, password\n- [ ] Verify method logs in to registry if credentials provided\n- [ ] Verify method pushes image to registry\n- [ ] Verify method returns push result with pushed_image\n- [ ] Verify error handling for authentication failures\n- [ ] Verify error handling for push failures\n\n**Verification**: Push test image and verify success\n\n---\n\n### Task 18: Implement unit tests for PublishRuntime.publish\n- [ ] Create tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py\n- [ ] Test successful publish with agentcube provider\n- [ ] Test successful publish with k8s provider\n- [ ] Test missing metadata file raises FileNotFoundError\n- [ ] Test invalid metadata raises ValidationError\n- [ ] Test invalid provider raises ValueError\n- [ ] Test verbose mode enables debug logging\n- [ ] Verify test coverage > 80%\n\n**Verification**: Run `pytest tests/runtime/test_publish_run